00:50:18,265 --> 00:50:20,308
who was not the popular choice,

691
00:50:20,434 --> 00:50:22,811
who was not somebody
you'd think of for the role,

692
00:50:22,895 --> 00:50:28,483
as against a proven star like Joan Crawford,
