00:50:30,945 --> 00:50:34,447
and was even talking to the costume
designer about her wardrobe.

695
00:50:34,699 --> 00:50:37,534
I wouldn't have wanted
to be in her house that night

696
00:50:37,618 --> 00:50:40,620
- when she learned the truth.
