855
01:02:26,660 --> 01:02:28,577
But look what it's doing to you.

856
01:02:28,662 --> 01:02:30,746
I love the army.

857
01:02:31,790 --> 01:02:34,083
But it sure doesn't love you.

858
01:02:35,293 --> 01:02:37,586
A man loves a thing,
that don't mean it's gotta love him back.

859
01:02:37,671 --> 01:02:43,926
I was just wondering
when you were at home and Clift was around,

860
01:02:44,010 --> 01:02:46,095
were you making the movie then?

861
01:02:46,179 --> 01:02:47,179
Did he...

862
01:02:47,264 --> 01:02:49,682
- What, From Here to Eternity?
- Yeah.

863
01:02:49,766 --> 01:02:50,766
Well, he...

864
01:02:50,851 --> 01:02:53,102
Was there any discussion about...

