01:03:37,731 --> 01:03:43,486
which he was blowing in the middle
of dinner and getting everybody very upset.

876
01:03:47,157 --> 01:03:48,949
This is working on the role, right?

877
01:03:49,034 --> 01:03:53,496
Well, no, this was after he had finished
and he couldn't get out of the role.

