01:04:17,938 --> 01:04:22,358
and he was on the floor with blood
gushing out of his nose, clutching his bugle.

884
01:04:22,442 --> 01:04:27,696
And then the matre d' came over and
thought it would be a good idea if we left.

885
01:04:29,533 --> 01:04:32,785
This isn't that kind, gentle fellow
I was talking about earlier.

886
01:04:32,869 --> 01:04:34,203
- Who, Clift?
- Clift.

887
01:04:34,287 --> 01:04:36,914
He had his moments both ways, I'd say.

