01:04:42,712 --> 01:04:46,048
So many of these people are...

890
01:04:46,132 --> 01:04:49,051
I don't want to talk about that,
but passed away.

891
01:04:49,135 --> 01:04:52,054
So few people are left.

892
01:04:52,138 --> 01:04:54,974
- That's amazing how few there are.
- Yeah.

893
01:04:55,642 --> 01:04:57,643
You'd better go.

894
01:04:59,312 --> 01:05:03,691
What's interesting to me is how this movie,
watching it, still holds up.

895
01:05:07,571 --> 01:05:13,492
I don't know what to attribute it to other than
